  "title": "Student Care Teacher | Bedok North | 5 Days | Up To $2.4K - 4461",
  "description": "<p><strong>Student Care Teacher</strong><br />Salary: $1800 - $2400<br />Working Days: Mon - Fri 12 - 8pm & Sat 9am - 2:30pm<br />Address: Bedok North (15 min walk from Bedok MRT Station/ Bedok Reservoir MRT Station)<br /></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide daily care, supervision, and guidance to children in the centre</li><li>Fetch children from schools or designated pick-up points</li><li>Support children with homework and school-related work</li><li>Conduct simple enrichment or tuition activities when required</li><li>Assist with daily routines, including tea breaks and mealtimes </li><li>Support the planning and execution of holiday programmes and activities</li><li>Communicate daily updates or observations to supervisors</li><li>Maintain general cleanliness and housekeeping standards within the centre</li><li>Follow centre policies and safety procedures at all times</li><li>Carry out any other duties as assigned by the Centre Supervisor/ Management</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>With student care teacher experiences preferred. </li></ul><p><br /><strong>Email: supreme.jacksontan@gmail.com</strong></p><p><strong>Tan Yong Zhi (Jackson) | Reg: R24124461</strong></p><p><strong>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd | EA No: 14C7279</strong></p>",
